@startuml
actor "Business admin" as Admin
participant "AdminPlatformView" as UI
participant "AdminPlatformController" as API
participant "AdminPlatformService" as SVC
Admin -> UI: open /admin/platform
UI -> API: GET /api/admin/platform/kpis
API -> SVC: dashboard(token, filters)
SVC --> API: KpiDashboardResponse
API --> UI: KPI tiles + alerts
Admin -> UI: save integration SLA
UI -> API: PUT /api/admin/platform/integrations/WMS_1C
API -> SVC: save settings with reasonCode
SVC --> API: IntegrationSettingsResponse
API --> UI: STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_PLATFORM_INTEGRATION_SAVED
@enduml